						<summary>

						<p>This records a gift of money to the temple of Iruṅgōḷīśvaramuḍaiya-nāyanār at Kōyāṟṟūr <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Uttamaśōḻapuram in Vaḍapuli-nāḍu a division of Perumbāṇappāḍi in Jayaṅgoṇḍaśōḻa-maṇḍalam by Akaḷaṅka-Sīyagaṅgaṉ <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Śittavaḍadēvaṉ for the merit of the chief Uttamaśōḻagaṅgar <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Veṭṭum Amarābaraṇar.</p>						

